text: Wanda Vázquez Garced is a Puerto Rican lawyer and politician. She was the 14th governor of Puerto Rico from August 7, 2019 to January 2, 2021. She also was Secretary of Justice from 2017 to 2019. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:1960 births Category:Governors of Puerto Rico Category:Lawyers Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from San Juan, Puerto Rico
